T1  - A Multiplier Adjustment Method for the Generalized Assignment Problem
AU  - Fisher, Marshall L.
AU  - Jaikumar, R.
AU  - Van Wassenhove, Luk N.
Y1  - 1986/09/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.32.9.1095
