T1  - The Channel Intermediary Selection Decision: A Model and an Application
AU  - Rangan, V. Kasturi
AU  - Zoltners, Andris A.
AU  - Becker, Robert J.
Y1  - 1986/09/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/09/01
