TY  - JOUR
T1  - Optimal Capacity Expansion Planning When There are Learning Effects
AU  - Hiller, Randall S.
AU  - Shapiro, Jeremy F.
Y1  - 1986/09/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/09/01
